com.ibm.mq.explorer.ms0s.mqsceditor.events

Interface IMQSCCommandEventListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MQSCContentOutlinePage.ContentProvider, MQSCDocumentModel

    public interface IMQSCCommandEventListener

    This defines an interface for relevant listeners to receive MQSC Command Events. These are events that are emitted from the fine grained parsing of the MQSC document. This was intended to enable the outline view to update asynchronously instead of when the document is saved. However, these events are emitted at least twice for each document, and so the Outline view is inconsistent.
